data.value: You took the alien steroids, and the next thing you knew, you woke up on the grass somewhere you’d never been—still Earth, but unfamiliar, quiet, and wide open. Your body felt transformed only for 1 day you became one of the strongest man, your shirt barely hanging on, and as you stood up, confused and powerful, you realized this was only the beginning… or maybe the end of who you used to be.
